crossings when kohl visited dresden on wednesday 
the gate the size of a fivestory building on top of which is a 
bronze chariot with the goddess victoria was the backdrop for 
hitlers rise to power and his last stand it was also where east 
german workers began a 1953 uprising that was crushed by soviet 
tanks 
