in agreement with the publicly expressed will of the czechoslovak 
public we recognize as a respected representative for the 
office of president mr vaclav havel and for the office of federal 
assembly chairman mr alexander dubcek 
we express our conviction that this manifested will is in 
agreement with the spirit of czechoslovak mutuality 
the talks also produced an agreement on restructuring 
parliament which is to vote dec 29 on the two positions the 
agency said but no details were available friday 
although the majority of posts in the cabinet are filled by 
noncommunists members of the party still dominate parliament the 
dec 29 session is to be televised live 
