tis the season to be traditional but silly 
santas laughing reindeer and teddy bears are arriving in mailboxes 
nationwide this year as christmas card makers appeal to a trend in 
card buying that transcends race religion and sex humor 
those who like the offbeat can send a card showing cow udders 
singing a christmas carol or santa kicking a football through the 
antlers of a laughing reindeer 
while the majority of the 23 billion christmas cards sent this 
